{{Quote|And everyone knows the Night Herald is just a myth you tell the larvae to make them regurgitate.|C-3PO translating Killik speech|<ref name="Dark Nest II: The Unseen Queen">''[[Dark Nest II: The Unseen Queen]]''</ref>}}
'''Night Herald''' was a [[Killik/Legends|Killik]] title, bestowed upon Killiks and [[Joiner]]s alike. It was given to [[Welk]] when he became a [[Joiner]] of the [[Gorog]] nest, becoming the guardian of the nest's Unseen Queen, [[Lomi Plo]]. Upon Welk's [[Battle of Kr|death]] at the hands of [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], [[Alema Rar]], herself having become recently Joined, took up the mantle of Night Herald until her defeat at the hands of [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] and the destruction of the Dark Nest.

